cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR

The paper deals with image manipulation detection using semantic segmentation, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on achieving state-of-the-art performance and maintaining robustness to attacks suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
